Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生的那會兒喲 總是眼紅人家的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞭解啦 我也是過來人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在怎樣也不能在騎車的\N時候把尊敬的前輩甩下車而殺掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誰也沒有殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 答錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再來一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的不是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗 又答錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不答對的話就只有換那位可愛的小姐上場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快承認你殺了人 在調查記錄上簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:58.74,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:58.74,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:11.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:11.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:14.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:14.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:18.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:18.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:21.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:21.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:25.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:25.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:46.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:46.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:50.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:50.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
